commit.message:
Make the generation of c_uamqp.c reproducible (#144)

Creating c_uamqp.c varies depending on the build path and on
the filesystem (ordering of directory listing).
Avoid including absolute paths in the source file and list
pyx files using sort so that the output is stable.
